title: Syrian Army Seizes Key Height From Daesh Near Palmyra

organizations.name: syrian army seizes key height from daesh near palmyra syrian army

text:
Syrian Army Seizes Key Height From Daesh Near Palmyra © REUTERS/ 0 100 3 0 The Syrian army has retaken a strategic height from Daesh terrorists to the southeast of Palmyra, local media said Monday. 
DAMASCUS (Sputnik) — Syrian troops and pro-government militias have taken control over height 939.5, the top strategic point of the Al-Hayal range, the SANA news agency reported, citing a military source. 
The operation has wiped out numerous Daesh militants as well as destroying a large number of enemy military equipment, according to the source. ...
